      "content": "the thing is i cant really get a hold of my doctor until monday and i havent slept in like two days. i'm just really exhausted and worried i won't be able to function at work. if i take a little extra melatonin with the ambien tonight, is it really gonna be that big of a deal? it's all just sleep stuff anyway, right?",
